OL,3,CThe higher fines parents face as
OL,4,Cgovernment bids to boost school
OL,5,Cattendance
OL,7,FITV News Political Correspondent Libby
OL,8,FWiener explains the higher fines and
OL,9,Fnew rules parents who take their
OL,10,Fchildren out of school will face
OL,12,FBy Rachel Dixon, Multimedia Producer
OL,14,FParents in England will face higher
OL,15,Ffines for taking their children out of
OL,16,Fschool without permission, under new
OL,17,Fgovernment rules.
