OL,3,CThe higher fines parents face as
OL,4,Cgovernment bids to boost school
OL,5,Cattendance
OL,7,FThe Department for Education (DfE) has
OL,8,Fsaid a fine must be considered if a
OL,9,Fchild misses five days of school for
OL,10,Funauthorised absence.
OL,12,FIt's part of a government campaign to
OL,13,Fdrive up school attendance as numbers
OL,14,Fhave not returned to normal after
OL,15,Fslipping during the pandemic.
OL,17,FAlmost 400,000 penalty notices were
OL,18,Fissued to parents in England in 2022-
OL,19,F23 for unauthorised school absences -
OL,20,Fwhich is much higher than pre-pandemic
OL,21,Flevels.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/14
