OL,3,CThe higher fines parents face as
OL,4,Cgovernment bids to boost school
OL,5,Cattendance
OL,7,FHere's how parents will be impacted by
OL,8,Fthe new rules.
OL,10,FWhat are the new fines ?
OL,12,FSchool absence fines currently start
OL,13,Fat #60, rising to #120, if they are
OL,14,Fnot paid within 21 days.
OL,16,FBut the DfE has said fines will now
OL,17,Fstart at #80, rising to #160.
OL,19,FA fine must be considered if a child
OL,20,Fmisses five days of school for
OL,21,Funauthorised absence.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G3/14
