OL,3,CThe higher fines parents face as
OL,4,Cgovernment bids to boost school
OL,5,Cattendance
OL,7,FWhile the system has always been in
OL,8,Fplace, a national framework will be
OL,9,Fused to help tackle inconsistencies in
OL,10,Ftheir use.
OL,12,FWho decides whether a fine will be
OL,13,Fissued?
OL,15,FWhile schools should initially work
OL,16,Fwith parents to encourage attendance
OL,17,Fthrough meetings or contracts, which
OL,18,Fset out targets for children coming in
OL,19,Fto school, if this fails a fixed
OL,20,Fpenalty notice will be issued.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G4/14
