OL,3,CThe higher fines parents face as
OL,4,Cgovernment bids to boost school
OL,5,Cattendance
OL,7,FThese can only be issued by a
OL,8,Fheadteacher or someone authorised by
OL,9,Fthem (a deputy or assistant head), a
OL,10,Flocal authority officer or the police.
OL,12,FSchool councils set out the rules and
OL,13,Fguidance on when a fixed penalty fine
OL,14,Fcan be issued, under a code of conduct.
OL,16,FWhat would likely lead to a fine?
OL,18,FThe fines are not meant to punish
OL,19,Fchildren with physical or mental
OL,20,Fhealth issues, the education minister
OL,21,Fhas said.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G5/14
