OL,7,F"Not only does it affect the child's
OL,8,Feducation but it means teachers then
OL,9,Fhave to spend time helping children to
OL,10,Fcatch-up with lost learning. If
OL,11,Feverybody did this it would be chaos."
OL,13,FLocal councils publish their guidance
OL,14,Fon what would lead to a fine.
