OL,3,CThe higher fines parents face as
OL,4,Cgovernment bids to boost school
OL,5,Cattendance
OL,7,FFor example, Medway Council, in Kent
OL,8,Fsays a child has to be absent for five
OL,9,Fschool days within six weeks,
OL,10,Fpersistently coming in late, after the
OL,11,Fregister is taken or miss an exam when
OL,12,Fthe date of it was previously
OL,13,Fpublished.
OL,15,FIf these are not paid, it can lead to
OL,16,Fa court case.
