OL,7,FWill the fines help absences?
OL,9,FIt is hoped upping the charges and
OL,10,Fstandardising the national rules will
OL,11,Fhelp return school attendance to pre-
OL,12,Fpandemic levels.
OL,14,FHowever some feel targeting parents
OL,15,Ffinancially, rather than focusing on
OL,16,Fimproving barriers families face does
OL,17,Fnot go far enough to stop the problem.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G9/14
