OL,4,Cgovernment bids to boost school
OL,5,Cattendance
OL,7,FEmily Hunt, Associate Director for
OL,8,FSocial Mobility and Vulnerable
OL,9,FLearners at the Education Policy
OL,10,FInstitute (EPI). said: "Increasing the
OL,11,Fcost of fines for parents whose
OL,12,Fchildren miss school is likely less
OL,13,Feffective than measures to support
OL,14,Ffamilies and tackle the root causes of
OL,15,Fabsence.
