OL,3,CThe higher fines parents face as
OL,4,Cgovernment bids to boost school
OL,5,Cattendance
OL,7,F"There is a risk that not only do
OL,8,Ffines fail to address the attendance
OL,9,Fbarriers that families face, but that
OL,10,Fthey are counter-productive through
OL,11,Fplacing additional strains on family
OL,12,Ffinances. Such punitive measures
OL,13,Fshould only be used as a last resort.
