OL,4,Cgovernment bids to boost school
OL,5,Cattendance
OL,7,F"We have previously called for
OL,8,Finvestment to improve both mental
OL,9,Fhealth provision in schools and
OL,10,Fsupport for children with SEND,
OL,11,Falongside the urgent need for a cross-
OL,12,Fgovernment child poverty strategy. We
OL,13,Falso need higher levels of funding for
OL,14,Fdisadvantaged children and a much
OL,15,Fstronger evidence base on why so many
OL,16,Fchildren are missing school."
