OL,7,FThe collected fines should first be
OL,8,Fused for administration of the penalty
OL,9,Fnotice system and prosecution, the
OL,10,Fgovernment guidance says.
OL,12,FAny surplus should be spent on
OL,13,Fattendance support, which is defined
OL,14,Fas any other activity to improve
OL,15,Fattendance, short of a penalty notice
OL,16,For prosecution.
